datoCmsKey.bio: Hannah Clarke Levine is a NYC-based actor, singer, and avid Jeopardy-watcher. She is passionate about new works and is currently originating the role of punk-rock goddess INGRID in the premiere workshop production of MacGyver: The Musical.
